reference "fig:Recommendation-algorithm-using"

\end_inset

.
 The adapted version of the algorithm broadly contains the next steps:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Get the followees (
\emph on
outgoing
\emph default
) of the target user.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Get the followers (
\emph on
incoming
